                                <rect key="frame" x="30" y="205" width="354" height="249.66666666666663"/>
                                <string key="text">Apptorney is the most comprehensive &amp; consolidated legal information platform in Zambia. It provides legal content that is properly linked, categorized and indexed for more efficient and user friendly searches. 

It’s a single source platform for Zambian Case Law, Legislations and subsidiary Legislations. Therefore, getting rid of all your legal headaches of gathering information from fragmented data sources. 

As part of our commitment to promoting access to justice and the rule of law in Zambia, access to Apptorney is now completely FREE. 

We are proud to bring to Zambians an innovative legal platform and with your support, we will keep innovating to make it one of the most advanced legal systems in the world. 

Please take some time to go through our Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. If you have any queries, please contact us using the details below.</string>
